Short SHA is the build identity. Same SHA = same code. This is what makes build-vs-retag deterministic (§11.2).
11.2 Build vs Retag — The Deterministic Rule
Build is triggered by a code change (new commit / new SHA). Retag is triggered by promotion (same SHA moving forward, or main merge stamping SemVer). Never docker build at promotion or at main merge.

